    <item>
      <title>加拿大主要铁路濒临停运，特鲁多敦促达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/trudeau-calls-on-railways-union-to-reach-deal-to-stave-off-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多呼吁加拿大两大铁路公司和工会工人达成协议，避免停工，企业表示停工将对加拿大和美国经济造成重大损害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/trudeau-calls-on-railways-union-to-reach-deal-to-stave-off-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 17:24:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
